title: Ground Control II: Operation Exodus
description:
Ground Control II: Operation Exodus delivers real-time strategy with the flair of an action game.

After losing the battle in space, the NSA is forced to retreat to its last stronghold. The situation is desperate, but for the NSA, destiny is at hand. Its only hope now lies in an ancient legend
